{"tid":1003981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮：除非美國與中國在3月1日前達成令人滿意的結果，否則美國將調高關稅。","createTime":"2019-02-01T06:01:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T09:14:10.000Z","uid":13663,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4587accd8b685f9ab1308f89b5ba385fbe76fcdf","tid":1003981,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T06:01:20.000Z","msg":"美中貿易談判拚大和解 川普：3月1日硬期限<br />\n中央社 &middot; 463人追蹤<br />\nThe Central News Agency 中央通訊社6 小時前<br />\n（中央社華盛頓31日綜合外電報導）白宮今天說，美國總統川普將3月1日視為與中國達成貿易協議的「硬期限」，屆時雙方若未達成協議，美國將上調中國商品的進口關稅。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報導，美中官員展開為期兩天的貿易會談後，白宮表示：「川普總統重申，在布宜諾斯艾利斯（Buenos Aires）達成的90天進程就是代表硬期限，除非美國與中國在3月1日前達成令人滿意的結果，否則美國將調高關稅。」（譯者：劉文瑜/核稿：盧映孜）1080201"},{"pid":"9544fd0517fcf3ee74ad44b06d3d76abc54b35a5","tid":1003981,"uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T06:02:00.000Z","msg":"美帝調高關稅，鄰國已成最大贏家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a0bf0e3b87554c48911efbd0fa410b489b5185f","tid":1003981,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T06:02:40.000Z","msg":"my fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f5c4963c2dc1d4c51b2c615cc3f708c495c008","tid":1003981,"uid":99962,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T06:03:23.000Z","msg":"侵侵玩到支支頭暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6153458f490db570bcb500a0a3231a0eb64d907","tid":1003981,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T06:15:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb42499c6927bd13c156d9da878cd3cd8f1a4cfa","tid":1003981,"uid":35205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T06:16:37.000Z","msg":"即係有滿意結果 稅都係會繼續收<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49aed8162dcb9a8dcb01f1537c30939f6a6a6290","tid":1003981,"uid":60529,"like":0,"disli